<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>98</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men yào zài jù huì de shān shàng jìng bài yé hé huá, wǒ men yào zài jù huì de shān shàng zàn měi yé hé huá.
 yīn wèi tā qū sàn le wǒ men xīn zhōng de chóu fán, yīn wèi tā dài lái le guāng míng hé píng ān,
 wǒ men yào huān yíng tā lái dào zhè lǐ, dēng shàng bǎo zuò zhí zhǎng wáng quán.
 shèng guò le chóu dí cì xià zhù fú, tā de róng yào chōng mǎn shèng shān.</lyrics>
<title>wǒ men yào zài jù huì de shān shàng 迦南98</title>
</song>